happened a long time ago.

40:22.520 --> 40:23.800
Thanks.

40:23.880 --> 40:28.400
Word of advice. Don't go falling
for any of your subordinates.

40:30.000 --> 40:37.000
I'll try my best. How's MDG ?
And Owen ? I haven't really talk...

40:37.160 --> 40:40.840
Talked to them, I know.
He's good. He's been promoted.

40:40.920 --> 40:44.480
- Meredith, she finally came out.
- What ?

40:44.560 --> 40:47.120
I'm kidding. Here.

40:51.480 --> 40:53.000
Thank you.

40:53.320 --> 40:56.760
You look different.
Not completely different, but...

40:59.720 --> 41:01.560
I lost a little weight,
maybe it's that, right ?

41:01.640 --> 41:03.960
Maybe. I've piled on the pounds.

41:04.040 --> 41:06.800
