my love of fried chicken.

41:06.880 --> 41:10.320
- John ?
- We got back together.

41:10.760 --> 41:12.720
Really ?

41:13.120 --> 41:15.240
Does that surprise you ?

41:15.840 --> 41:18.920
I donno. Maybe not.

41:19.000 --> 41:21.240
Do you know what, in many ways,
what happened between us

41:21.320 --> 41:23.360
was a good thing.
The break-up...

41:23.440 --> 41:26.280
- The large, filtered, tall, black ?
- That's me. Thank you.

41:26.360 --> 41:28.600
The whole thing has just made me
think about what I wanted,

41:28.680 --> 41:30.480
what I needed in a relationship
to make it work,

41:30.560 --> 41:32.840
so in many ways, I'm quite thankful
that you came into my life

41:32.920 --> 41:36.160
and fucked it up
'cause it's better, now.

41:37.600 --> 41:39.200
