to suggest that.

41:49.960 --> 41:55.280
Not surprising. We came to fully
understand our wants and our needs.

41:56.200 --> 41:57.360
You've been here too long,

41:57.440 --> 41:59.240
you're even starting
to sound like an American.

41:59.320 --> 42:01.080
Large, soy milk iced coffee ?

42:01.160 --> 42:03.960
If I meet Chris Pratt
down at Fitness First

42:04.040 --> 42:07.920
I can jerk him off to my heart's
content and that's completely fine.

42:09.160 --> 42:13.080
