- It's hardly Minecraft.

42:51.120 --> 42:54.720
Okay, but it could still
end up making us some money.

42:54.800 --> 42:57.360
Stereotyped, cliche-ridden dross.

42:57.920 --> 43:01.080
Or my personal favorite,
what the fuck is the point ?

43:01.160 --> 43:02.680
Why do you read what people say ?

43:02.760 --> 43:05.320
- Don't you ?
- Yeah, but I don't care.

43:05.400 --> 43:08.160
Anyway, making money
was never the point.

43:08.240 --> 43:10.480
What was the point ?

43:12.640 --> 43:18.600
I feel like it doesn't make sense
for us to do it anymore.

43:19.880 --> 43:21.360
Together.

43:23.560 --> 43:26.040
Okay, I'm gonna ask you something.

43:26.120 --> 43:29.200
Were you ever actually in love
with me ?

43:33.400 --> 43:36.560
Yes, I think so.

43:37.600 --> 43:39.880
I certainly
loved the idea of us...

43:39.960 --> 43:42.240
'Cause I could've made it work.

43:42.320 --> 43:46.520
When I said I wanted to
be monogamous with you, I meant it.

43:46.600 --> 43:50.200
I didn't want you to make a promise
you couldn't keep.

43:50.280 --> 43:53.160
Fuck you. How do you know
I wouldn't keep it ?

43:53.240 --> 43:55.040
That's not why we broke up, we
just weren't right for each other.

43:55.120 --> 43:57.880
- No, how do you know that ?
- I did, I do.

43:57.960 --> 44:02.080
