hard graft to make it work.

44:35.680 --> 44:39.800
I don't want to seem
like a cunt, but you are a coward.

44:39.880 --> 44:43.720
I don't think that's fair.
I couldn't trust you, any more.

44:43.800 --> 44:46.240
And I don't know
what hard graft means,

44:46.320 --> 44:47.760
