for the next thing.

45:10.600 --> 45:15.760
You are. I know you.
You run away and you are a coward.

45:15.840 --> 45:18.680
You were a coward with me,
you were a coward with Richard.

45:18.760 --> 45:21.040
You come across a few potholes
in the road,

45:21.120 --> 45:22.520
and instead of trying to navigate
through it,

45:22.600 --> 45:25.160
you slam your brakes on,
and you run the other direction.

45:25.240 --> 45:28.560
