I just want you to be happy.

48:06.000 --> 48:07.400
Why ?

48:08.040 --> 48:10.600
Why ? 'Cause I love you.

48:16.320 --> 48:19.160
Look, don't stay in Denver.
Come back,

48:19.240 --> 48:21.640
